      • onDestroy

        protected void onDestroy()
        Description copied from class: BluetoothLeBaseActivity
        When the final instance of BluetoothLeBaseActivity is going to be destroyed, BluetoothLeBaseActivity.mBluetoothLeService should be stopped and unbind. And BluetoothLeBaseActivity.mBluetoothLeServiceBindActivity will be assigned null. So, please make sure that all activities using BLE extend from BluetoothLeBaseActivity.
        Overrides:
        onDestroy in class BluetoothLeBaseActivity
